[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator Cookie 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本存在安全绕过漏洞。当用户启用 JavaScript 且已选择\"仅接受来自正浏览页面同一服务器之 Cookie\"选项时，浏览器仍不会对 Cookie 设置行为发出警告。攻击者可利用恶意网页绕过 Cookie 同源策略，跨站设置或窃取用户 Cookie，导致用户隐私泄露或会话劫持。漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"停止使用 Netscape Communicator 4.x，升级至 Mozilla Firefox 或其它现代浏览器，并在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。对于仍必须使用 Netscape 的场景，可在浏览器首选项中关闭 JavaScript 功能（Edit → Preferences → Advanced → Scripts & Plugins → 取消启用 JavaScript）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0573","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0349","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP LIST 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 的 FTP 服务中的 list (ls) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的 FTP 列表请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS，攻击条件低，危害严重，建议及时安装安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0349"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.357","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-003 提供的补丁（Q223783），或升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用 FTP 服务（停止 MSFTPSVC 服务），或限制匿名用户对 FTP 根目录的写入权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ188348","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/IIS%20Remote%20FTP%20Exploit/DoS%20Attack.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0349.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_ftp_crash.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0572","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0808","title":"ISC DHCP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC DHCP 服务器（dhcpd）1.0 和 2.0 版本存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 DHCP 服务器发送包含超长选项字段的恶意数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务，甚至可能利用该漏洞执行任意代码。该漏洞影响大量使用 ISC DHCP 服务的网络环境，攻击条件简单，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0808"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.993","remediation":"建议立即升级 ISC DHCP 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 dhcpd 1.0/2.0 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 DHCP 服务器 UDP 67/68 端口的访问，仅允许受信任的子网段通信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-053.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925960&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0571","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0348","title":"Microsoft IIS ASP 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 的 ASP 缓存机制存在信息泄露漏洞。当两个虚拟服务器共享同一物理目录时，ASP 脚本缓存未能正确隔离不同虚拟服务器之间的数据，导致攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制请求，获取同一物理目录下其他虚拟站点的敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 IIS 版本，公开利用难度较低，可能导致网站配置文件、源代码等敏感数据泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0348"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.237","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft KB Q197003 安全更新（包含于 Windows NT 4.0 Security Rollup Package），该更新修复了 ASP 脚本缓存在虚拟服务器间的隔离问题。如无法安装补丁，应将每个虚拟服务器配置为使用独立的物理目录，避免不同虚拟主机共用同一目录；也可在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 ASP 脚本文件缓存作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ197003","http://www.osvdb.org/930","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0348.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0570","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0807","title":"Netscape Directory Server 安装过程敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Directory Server 在安装过程中存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。安装程序将管理员密码、配置凭证等敏感数据以明文方式保存在本地文件中，且未设置充分的访问权限控制。本地攻击者可通过读取这些文件获取敏感信息，进而可能提升权限或获取目录服务器的管理访问权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Netscape Directory Server，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0807"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.883","remediation":"由于 Netscape Directory Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至 389 Directory Server、Red Hat Directory Server 或 OpenLDAP 等现代替代品。迁移前应立即检查并收紧安装目录文件权限（如 /usr/netscape/server4/ 等），移除 world-readable 权限并清理安装过程中遗留的 .inf/.log/响应文件等含明文凭据的临时文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0807"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0569","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0347","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Invalid Byte 跨框架访问漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01 及 5.0.1 版本中存在跨帧访问安全漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 \"about:\" JavaScript URL 中插入 \"%01\" 无效字节字符，可绕过同源策略限制，跨域读取目标系统本地文件内容或实施网页伪造欺骗。该漏洞影响面广泛，攻击者只需诱使用户访问构造的恶意网页即可触发，无需任何身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0347"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.110","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 1 或更高版本（如 IE 5.5/6.0），以消除 %01 字符跨域访问漏洞。若无法升级，可临时将 Internet 区域安全级别设为\"高\"并禁用 Active Scripting，以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91745430007021&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91756771207719&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19156","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0347","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0347.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mpqm-r86r-845w/GHSA-mpqm-r86r-845w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0347.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000498.txt","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0568","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0806","title":"Sun Solaris dtprintinfo 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 dtprintinfo 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该程序位于 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，在处理特制输入时未正确验证缓冲区边界，导致可被利用覆盖内存数据。本地攻击者可通过向 dtprintinfo 传递超长参数触发溢出，进而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0806"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.767","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 107080-01（SPARC 平台）或 107081-01（x86 平台）修复 dtprintinfo 缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法打补丁，立即移除 dtprintinfo 的 setuid 位：chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，或限制仅管理员可执行：chmod 700 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo。如不需要 CDE 打印功能可直接删除该二进制文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6552","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0567","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0346","title":"PHP PHP/FI mlog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0346 是 PHP 的 mlog CGI 脚本中存在的一个任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标服务器上该脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用参数注入的方式读取服务器上的任意敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 PHP 版本，攻击条件低（无需认证、远程利用）。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0346"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.993","remediation":"升级至 PHP 3.0.17 或更高版本（已修复该 CGI 漏洞），或删除/禁用服务器上的 mlog CGI 脚本。若无法升级，请在 Web 服务器配置中禁止执行 /cgi-bin/php/fi/mlog 等路径，并设置文件系统权限限制 CGI 进程仅访问必要目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3397","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0346","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0346.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/mtesauro/owasp-wte/blob/e4c016caf67d59634f309f2a1feeed7dc9515abe/temp-projects/spikeproxy/contents/opt/owasp/spikeproxy/scan_database.db","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0564","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0564.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0345","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 ICMP Jolt 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 的 ICMP 协议处理存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过向目标系统发送特制的分片 ICMP 数据包（即 Jolt 攻击），触发系统在处理畸形 IP 分片重组时产生资源耗尽或内核崩溃，导致目标系统蓝屏死机或完全停止响应。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 版本，属于经典的 IP 分片攻击方式。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0345"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.867","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-035 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6 及以上版本；Windows 95 用户应安装 Winsock2 更新。如无法打补丁，建议在网络边界防火墙或主机 IPSec 策略中丢弃恶意分片 ICMP 数据包，防止畸形 IP 分片到达目标系统。彻底解决需升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/62170","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0345","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0345.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pwf4-g7fv-h2w4/GHSA-pwf4-g7fv-h2w4.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7c1bf0db-8de4-4873-82bc-3461101fb8a2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0564.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0561","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0342","title":"Linux PAM 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux PAM（可插拔认证模块）存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在/tmp目录下创建符号链接指向目标文件，诱导使用了共享库的PAM模块在提升权限的过程中读写临时文件，从而利用条件竞争漏洞覆盖系统关键文件或执行任意代码，最终获取root权限。该漏洞影响多种Linux发行版及使用了PAM模块的UNIX类系统，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，CVSS评分6.2，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0342"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.490","remediation":"建议升级 Linux PAM 至 0.64 及以上版本，该版本已修复临时文件竞争条件漏洞，改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件。旧版 Red Hat Linux 用户应安装 RHSA-1999:013 公告对应补丁。如无法升级，可限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，并启用严格的 umask 策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0342"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0560","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0341","title":"Debian Linux deliver 邮件程序本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 系统中的 mail 程序 \"deliver\" 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限，危害等级高，影响 Debian Linux 系统。建议及时安装厂商发布的安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0341"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.357","remediation":"升级 Linux 发行版至至少 Debian 3.0（Woody）以上版本，该版本已移除有漏洞的 deliver 程序，改用更安全的邮件传输代理。如因特殊原因仍使用 deliver，立即将其 SUID 权限移除（chmod u-s /usr/bin/deliver），并迁移至 exim 或 postfix 等现代 MTA。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0559","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0340","title":"Slackware Linux crond 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 系统中 crond 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 crond 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞允许拥有本地账户的攻击者利用 crond 在处理参数时的内存边界校验缺陷，实现权限提升。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Slackware Linux 系统。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制本地用户对 crond 的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0340"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.243","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 至 3.4 及以上版本，该修复版本已修正 crond 程序在处理用户提交的计划任务参数时的边界检查缺陷，防止本地用户通过特制参数触发缓冲区溢出提权。如无法升级，可限制 crond 仅允许受信用户通过 `cron.allow` 文件控制访问，并移除 `/etc/cron.d` 中不必要的任务文件。同时检查 crond 二进制是否被替换，使用 `rpm -V` 或 `md5sum` 校验文件完整性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0340"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0558","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0558.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0339","title":"Sun Solaris libauth 库缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 libauth 认证库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该库函数传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得额外的系统权限，可能提升至 root 级别。该漏洞影响多个 Solaris 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账号才能发起利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0339"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.120","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 7 及以上），安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-xx（针对 libauth 库缓冲区溢出）。若无法升级，限制本地用户登录并启用最小权限原则，仅授权可信用户访问系统，同时监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0339"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0558.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0557","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0338","title":"IBM AIX 性能工具本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的许可软件产品性能工具存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该工具集的特权配置缺陷，通过执行特定命令获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用，无需用户交互。成功利用后攻击者可完全控制系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0338"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.000","remediation":"安装 IBM 针对该漏洞发布的 AIX APAR 补丁包，或升级至包含该修复的最新 AIX 维护级别（Maintenance Level）。临时缓解措施：以 root 用户执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/filemon /usr/bin/svmon /usr/bin/tprof` 移除受影响性能工具的 setuid 权限，并限制非授信用户对性能工具目录的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0338"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0556","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0337","title":"IBM AIX batch queue (bsh) 本地和远程权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统的批处理队列（bsh）存在权限提升漏洞。当网络打印服务启用时，本地或远程攻击者可通过向批处理队列提交特制任务，利用不充分的权限控制机制获取超出授权的系统访问权限，导致攻击者能够执行任意命令或操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0337"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.850","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 针对 AIX batch queue (bsh) 的安全补丁，升级到 AIX 4.3.3 及更高修复版本。如无法打补丁，可通过 `chsubserver -r bsh` 禁用 bsh 网络打印服务，或在 `/etc/security/user` 中限制 bsh 可执行权限仅为 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0337.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Wollny/CVE-1999-0337.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000050.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6dd5b793-7342-42d5-867d-37abc515d322.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml"}]